{"tid":1979252,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連登只一個網上論壇, 熱狗不停抺黑依度有乜居心?","createTime":"2020-04-19T09:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T06:36:44.000Z","uid":49643,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f19bbdac59904027c8508bea4157f8574948c249","tid":1979252,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:48:18.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3ea32bb6e1c194c2ec670c3a7892e856354717","tid":1979252,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:02:53.000Z","msg":"共產熱狗：連登太多革命派水軍，是大台，拆大台"},{"pid":"8a12bfa5ced307826e420c8f6642f6b05d714510","tid":1979252,"uid":208092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:54:11.000Z","msg":"點解我睇唔到有啲咁既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f797711be7b647d12c67cc34bfe51433c014c971","tid":1979252,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:03:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">借個位先 召喚聯署師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=0059b09b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面有好多為香港打定安全網既聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A部分請㩒入去呢度<br />\n記得睇埋啊，好撚緊要啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">【偽 &middot; 正視聽】得啦我知我洗咗你地版<br />\n召喚聯署師長文Q&amp;A就放喺度啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1981260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1981260</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"146eea724d80ffedf119d92276c5162045aed699","tid":1979252,"uid":122208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"熱狗都要食飯<br />\n五毛都係錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f079a002d31c4cedd333f85a8f0fb1d6a5bb648","tid":1979252,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"146eea724d80ffedf119d92276c5162045aed699","tid":1979252,"uid":122208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"熱狗都要食飯<br />\n五毛都係錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"加左價 7毛"},{"pid":"7bd183054d0e763c1834c0196547ce68be2d3b04","tid":1979252,"uid":122208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f079a002d31c4cedd333f85a8f0fb1d6a5bb648","tid":1979252,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"146eea724d80ffedf119d92276c5162045aed699","tid":1979252,"uid":122208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"熱狗都要食飯<br />\n五毛都係錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"加左價 7毛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T04:41:45.000Z","msg":"通漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年無啦，中共無水"},{"pid":"a971a71d09e324224393cf2f2c810444e44a3963","tid":1979252,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply